99
00:07:48.812 --> 00:07:49.302
Overall,

100
00:07:50.212 --> 00:07:52.972
I have reviewed my ministerial priorities in

101
00:07:53.112 --> 00:07:56.752
2026 and reconfirmed the priority performance

